  mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;
  mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin'>2012.07 - 2013.01&nbsp;&nbsp;深圳市蓝盾科技有限公司&nbsp;&nbsp;（6个月）</span>
